{
  "stem": "1415.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was in the wintertime, because I remember after the selection was over the snow was on the ground when we came out of our hiding place.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember the snow being all pink and red because there was so much blood on it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were so-- so many killings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everywhere you looked, everywhere you looked, the-- the-- the snow was all red.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is all I remember from-- from that selection.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after that, my grandmother was gone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My aunt was gone with her son and her husband.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I also found out-- actually, I found out recently that during that time, one of my aunts was hiding in her place, in her own home, with her three children and her husband.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the neighbors, the Poles, bludgeoned them with an ax, all five of them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I just found that out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I thought they went through the camps with us, but they didn't.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we ended up in a little-- in a-- in a little ghetto, and it was like a half a street long from a big town of 16,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were-- I was a child, so I-- I didn't do nothing at the time yet [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] until I got to be in the camp.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But somehow during that time, my brother got me involved with [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] some people that were going to the-- to the railroad tracks.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were working there and loading-- loading up-- because our town had a [POLISH], which is a brick factory.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were loading bricks at-- at that-- at that-- on the loading docks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I found that there were quite a few children.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
